    <h4>What is a typical day in your life at Bank of America?</h4>
    <p><strong>9:00 &ndash; 9:30 AM:</strong> Arrive at desk, review overnight news 
      and emails.</p>
    <p><strong>10:00 AM:</strong> Team meeting with senior bankers to discuss 
      strategic options that can be presented to the CEO and the Board the following 
      day.</p>
    <p><strong>10:30 AM:</strong> Team meeting with other associates /analysts 
      to discuss client deliverables and develop timeline and allocate work.</p>
    <p><strong>10:30 &ndash; 12:30 PM:</strong> Prepare financial model and start putting 
      together preliminary slides for the presentation. Conduct research on the 
      industry, sector and company in order to complete the financial model and 
      slides.</p>
    <p><strong>12:30 &ndash; 1:00 PM:</strong> Pickup lunch</p>
    <p><strong>1:00 &ndash; 1:30 PM:</strong> Discuss and finalize model with junior 
      team.</p>
    <p><strong>1:30 &ndash; 5:00 PM:</strong> Work on preparing draft of presentation.</p>
    <p><strong>5:00 &ndash; 6:00 PM:</strong> Team meeting with junior team to review 
      presentation.</p>
    <p><strong>6:00 &ndash; 8:30 PM:</strong> Finalize model and presentation. Send 
      copies to senior team for review.</p>
    <p><strong>8:30 &ndash; 9:30 PM:</strong> Quick run in the gym followed by dinner.</p>
    <p><strong>9:30 &ndash; 10:30 PM:</strong> Incorporate any comments received. Send 
      out revised version for final review.</p>
    <h4>What is your current assignment and primary responsibilities?</h4>
    <p>I am part of the Media Investment Banking team. Current assignments include 
      M&amp;A and financial advisory deals and client pitches in European Newspaper, 
      Publishing and Online Media sub-sectors. I am responsible for coordinating 
      with all the teams &ndash; clients, senior bankers, debt and equity capital markets, 
      legal counsel and other external parties depending on the nature of the 
      project. The role includes developing a project schedule, assigning specific 
      roles and executing within tough timelines </p>
